<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.211341>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 – 30. Male genitalia of Zaretis itys (Cramer, 1777) and Zaretis itylus (Westwood, 1850). 21 – 25. Z. itys. 21. Lateral view, valva, aedeagus removed; 22. Gnathos and uncus, ventral view; 23. Gnathos and uncus, posterior view; 24. Valva, lateral view; 25. Aedeagus, lateral view; 26 – 30. Z. itylus. 26. Lateral view, valva, aedeagus removed; 27. Gnathos and uncus, ventral view; 28. Gnathos and uncus, posterior view; 29. Valva, lateral view; 30. Aedeagus, lateral view. Scale bar = 0.5 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/211341/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

